            <p class="lead">A single party can end your Airbnb business. That is not an exaggeration. GTA municipalities now use <strong>demerit point systems</strong> that can suspend or revoke your short-term rental license after just one serious incident. Noise violations in <a href="/blog/burlington-airbnb-short-term-rental-rules-2026">Burlington</a> earn 5 demerit points, and 7 points triggers a license suspension of up to 6 months.</p>
