              <p>The person making the reservation says someone else will be staying. Third-party bookings violate Airbnb's terms of service and are a classic party setup where the account holder avoids accountability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Vague Trip Purpose</h4>
              <p>When asked about their visit, they avoid specifics or give non-answers like "just hanging out" or "getting together with some people." Legitimate travelers readily share their reason for visiting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
