          <h2 id="noise-monitoring">Noise Monitoring Technology</h2>
          <p>Noise monitors are the single most effective party prevention tool available to hosts. These devices measure sound levels inside your property without recording conversations, making them privacy-compliant and legal in Ontario.</p>

          <div class="points-table">
            <table>
              <thead>
